# 🛡️ Inhibitor Killing

Inhibitor cannot kill during Sabotages.

  • Max
    • Set the Maximum amount of Inhibitors that can be in a match
  • Kill Cooldown
    • Set how long the Inhibitor needs to wait to perform a kill
